{"tid":422891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買黃金變一袋泥沙 強國男尖沙嘴遇非洲老千中伏","createTime":"2017-10-03T12:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T12:37:24.000Z","uid":136994,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"77dd3071c8b3cb3dc0aae5442292acb9f5114fd6","tid":422891,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:33:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171003/57287349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171003%2F57287349&d=0h42LnngE9u5w8NSj%2FaLYozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=296096e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171003%2F57287349&h=f6a6478b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171003/57287349</a><br />\n<br />\n晚上約6時半，一名內地男子來港與2名非洲裔男子交易黃金，並相約到尖沙嘴彌敦道50號金域假日酒店見面。其間對方打開載有黃金的背囊供內地男驗貨，內地男查看後付款2萬元人民幣(折合約2.39萬港元)給對方，2名非洲裔男子收錢後即離開。詎料內地男再打開背囊卻發現黃金變了泥沙，懷疑遭騙徒偷龍轉鳳報警。警方到場調查案件，一度在附近兜截疑人，但未有發現。"},{"pid":"b5a268b1035c23dc851e591028aaa068c1af782c","tid":422891,"uid":32655,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"非洲男：屌，d 錢假既？"},{"pid":"4813448d7eb8c5ecd9db5ed48c0db0931f6f1e16","tid":422891,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"力架好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1572fe50e62ba1c463cb1dea24965773f5e079e","tid":422891,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"兩萬蚊一袋黃金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}